<div class="singup-second  padding-bottom-category">
  <div id="confirmation2"></div>
  <%= form_for("user", :url => user_registration_path, :html => {:id => "sign_up", :class => "sign-up-form-checkout"}) do |f| %>
    <div class="col-md-6 checkout-field">
      <label>First Name:</label>
      <%= f.text_field :first_name, :autofocus => true, :placeholder => "First Name", :class => "required" %>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-6 checkout-field">
      <label>Last Name:</label>
      <%= f.text_field :last_name, :autofocus => true, :placeholder => "Last Name", :class => "required" %>
    </div>
      <div class="col-md-6 checkout-field">
      <label>Email:</label>
      <%= f.email_field :email, :autofocus => true, :placeholder => "Email", :class => "required" %>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-6 checkout-field">
      <label>Password:</label>
      <%= f.password_field :password, :placeholder => "Password", :class => "required" %>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-6 checkout-field">
      <label>Password Confirmation:</label>
      <%= f.password_field :password_confirmation, :placeholder => "Password Confirmation" , :class => "required"%>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-6 checkout-field">
      <label>Your School:</label>
      <%= f.text_field :school_name, :autofocus => true, :placeholder => "Your School", :class => "search-keyword" %>

    </div>
    <div class="col-md-12 checkout-field">
      <p class="text-center">By clicking Sign Up you agree to the <a href="<%= term_of_service_path %>">Terms of Service</a> and <a href="<%= privacy_policy_path %>">Privacy Policy</a></p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-12 submit-button">
      <button>Sign up</button>
    </div>
    <img class="form-shadow" alt="Smiley face" src="/assets/shadow.png">
  <% end -%>
</div>
<div class="col-md-12 signup-content">
  <div class="row compus-content-container">
    <div class="col-md-12">
      <p class="order-heading">CampusBite offers a ton of benefits for being a member.Here you can see some of the best ones!</p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-12 compus-content-even">
      <p class="green-heading">Easy to Reorder Your Favorites-No Thinking Needed to Order</p>
      <div class="col-md-3 member-icon">
        <img class="logo-image" alt="Smiley face" src="/assets/bin.png">
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-9 member-content">
        <p>The CampusBite membership means that your orders are locked into history. If you have a favorite meal, you can just go in and select it quickly. Your favorite munchies, lunches, and dinners are ready to go with the click of a button.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-12 compus-content-odd">
      <div class="col-md-9 col-md-offset-3 deals-category">
        <h5>You Get the deals - cha-ching!</h5>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-3 member-icon">
        <img class="logo-image" alt="Smiley face" src="/assets/sale.png">
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-9 member-content">
        <p>When you are a CampusBite member, you will receive the best in money saving offers including discounts on everything and new coupons as soon as they come out of the marketing teams oven. We know you love saving money, and we want to make sure you do!</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-12 compus-content-even">
      <div class="col-md-9 col-md-offset-3 deals-category">
        <h5>store your address</h5>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-3 member-icon">
        <img class="logo-image" alt="Smiley face" src="/assets/sale-1.png">
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-9 member-content">
        <p>Your address for work and home is saved in our secured system, so you do not have to remind us where to go, we already know. This is how we saveyou even more time!</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-12 compus-content-odd">
      <div class="col-md-9 col-md-offset-3 deals-category">
        <h5>store your payment information</h5>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-3 member-icon">
        <img class="logo-image" alt="Smiley face" src="/assets/sale3.png">
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-9 member-content">
        <p>You can quickly order without having to find your debitor credit card. We securely store your information so you do not have to worry about it getting out there, just another way we make your life easier.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <img class="checkout-shadow" alt="Smiley face" src="/assets/shadow.png">
</div>

<script type="text/javascript">
  $(document).ready(function(){

    $(".search-keyword").typeahead([
      {
        name: 'Schools',
        remote: '/schools/search.json?keyword=%QUERY'
      }
    ]);
    $(".sign-up-form-checkout").validate();
    $(".sign-up-form-checkout").on('submit', function(e) {
      $("#sign-up").addClass("active");
      $(".user-information-tab li.sign-up").addClass("active");
      e.preventDefault(); // prevent native submit
      $(this).ajaxSubmit({
          target: '#confirmation2',
          dataType: 'html',
          success: function(result) {
            $(".checkout-btn-link").click();
          },
          error: function(jqxhr) {

            $("#confirmation2").html("<div class='alert alert-danager'><a class='close' data-dismiss='alert'>&#215;</a>" +jqxhr.responseText+"</div>");
            $("#confirmation2").hide();
            $("#confirmation2").fadeIn(500);
          }
      });
    });
  });
</script>